title: Burn Halo - Burn Halo (2009)
description:
Burn Halo is the debut album by American rock band Burn Halo. The album was set for release in 2008 through Island Records, but after the album was completed Island elected not to release it. It was released on March 31, 2009 through Rawkhead Rekords.
